    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The engine runs smoothly with no mechanical issues to report, and the transmission provides consistent, reliable shifting. The interior is clean, though it shows some minor wear consistent with regular use. On the exterior, the paint still holds a nice shine, although there are a few small stone chips and light scratches visible upon close inspection. Overall, it is a dependable car that is ready for its next owner to drive away without needing immediate repairs.",
