    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Experience automotive excellence with this breathtaking, mint-condition beauty! This car is truly in showroom state, looking and driving as if it just left the dealership for the first time. From the flawless paint to the pristine interior, every detail has been meticulously maintained, offering you a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in such perfect, like-new condition.",
