    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is, ideally for a buyer looking for a project or a source for parts. The exterior has significant rust on the rocker panels and wheel arches, along with faded paint and several large dents. Mechanically, the engine runs roughly and requires immediate diagnostic work, and the transmission shifts harshly between gears. The interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and a headliner that is beginning to sag, so please expect to invest time and resources into repairs.",
