    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-taken care of over the years\u2014perfect for someone who wants a reliable car without the brand-new price tag. It runs beautifully and is totally ready for its next big adventure with you! Come take it for a spin; I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have.",
