    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing. This example utilizes the Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and an M-Variable limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. The chassis is structurally sound with documented subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension geometry featuring updated bushings. Maintenance is up to date, including a recent valve adjustment and rod bearing service. While the finish shows honest road-going patina, the drivetrain remains tight, providing the linear torque and balanced handling characteristics essential to this platform's legendary status.",
      "price": 34500.0,
